\"http://www.nashvilleistalking.com/node/50997\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.nashvilleistalking.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville Is Talking</a>]</li><li>English Language Learners will hopefully be sent to centers closer to home instead of being shipped all over the county. [<a href=\"http://www.nashvillecitypaper.com/news.php?viewStory=61147\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">City Paper</a>]</li><li>Former state senator John Ford&#x2019;s corruption trial has been delayed again. He&#x2019;s on trial for allegedly swiping $800K from TennCare contractors. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/16747393/detail.html?rss=nash&amp;psp=news\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>The Titans have signed David Stewart, the starting right tackle who played all 16 games last season. No details on the contract yet, but they&#x2019;ll probably surface soon. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=8579832\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li></ul><p>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/j_u_l_i_e_t/2624078146/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">j u l i e t</a>.</p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/03/04/happy-hour-this-is-not-a-dog-toilet/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Happy Hour: This Is Not A Dog-Toilet\">Happy Hour: This Is Not A Dog-Toilet</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/07/18/happy-hour-dont-you-know-that-its-toxic/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link